casebody.data:
Donna S. SECK, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Theodore R. SHALACK, Defendant-Petitioner. C-755 September Term 2017
079628 Supreme Court of New Jersey. April 26, 2018

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001563-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
